# Feathers fly, Chaos reigns, Zombies chase. 🐔🧟‍♂️

**This is not your average VR game.** 

Dive into a fast-paced infection tag game where mutant chickens climb, glide, and infect in a dystopian world gone absolutely off the rails.

[media]

**Become a chicken and survive the outbreak... or spread it.?**  

Become a survivor or an Scratch, chase, and infect othes in a wild multiplayer chase 
— even if they were your “friends” two seconds ago.

[media]

**New: OBBY DRILL (Social Parkour Zone)**                                             

No matchmaking, no pressure — just pure movement and social chaos. Glide, hang out, or show off your parkour in the new Obby Drill.

[media]

**Earn Coins, XP, and Feathers** 

Every round counts. Whether you're running or infecting, you'll level up and earn rewards.

[media]

**Style your chicken, obviously** 

Costumes matter. Survive in style and flex your feathers.

[media]

This is not a drill. 

This is **the Chicking Dead**

Join our Discord to get access to exclusive events and the updates info!
discord.gg/chickingdead
